high_descs: Head around and walk towards the sofa.
Walk near the calculator.
Pick the remote from the sidetable.
Turn around and walk towards the calculator on the sidetable.
Place the remote on the sofa.
Head around and pick another caculator.
Head around and walk near the sidetable.
Place the caculator on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: To place the caculator on the round SideTable.

high_descs: Walk to the larger grey sofa.
Pick up the white caculator on the right of the box from the couch.
Walk to the round sidetable on the left.
Place the caculator on the sidetable.
Turn right to face the grey sofa again.
Pick up another caculator from the couch.
Turn to the sidetable on the left.
Put the caculator on the sidetable behind the previous one.
anns.task_desc: Put two caculators on the side table.

high_descs: Walk forward to the grey sofa.
Pick up the caculator from the sofa next to the lamp.
Turn left and face the round sidetable.
Set the caculator down on the sidetable.
Face the grey sofa again.
Pick up the caculator from the sofa next to the scissors.
Go to the sidetable.
Set the caculator down on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put two caculators on the round SideTable
